BT.models

Class CoordinateModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • BT.models.CoordinateModel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CDClassModel, LineModel, PetriNetModel, UCActor, UCUseCase

    public class CoordinateModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Model that describes each object on drawing pane. It stores basic data, that are used in each object, even in join edges.
    Author:
    Karel Hala
